        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "It seems that this behavior was originally introduced in <https://github.com/vim/vim/commit/019ff6825b54e31efc71faf3ce55cb78bac24d35>. There was no explanation for this change, but I think a possible reason is to avoid flicker in the popup menu. Since Nvim uses a compositor, redrawing windows will not cause flicker in the popup menu in Nvim, so these `pum_visible()` checks can now be removed.",
